des: WMUN is “The Talk of Muncie” based in Muncie, Indiana. Owned by Woof Boom Radio. A Fox Sports radio affiliate. Home to the Power Hour (local sports show weekdays 4-5pm), Delaware County high school football and basketball, the Colts, the Pacers, Indy 500, Ball State women's basketball, and more.
